00:06:55.048 --> 00:06:57.974
something that's hotter than
the ambient temperature.

00:06:57.974 --> 00:07:02.768
So we could imagine a world where T is

00:07:02.768 --> 00:07:05.623
greater than or equal to
our ambient temperature.

00:07:05.623 --> 00:07:09.570
So that means this is hot, or it's hotter,

00:07:09.057 --> 00:07:10.080
I guess we could say.

00:07:10.008 --> 00:07:10.095
So if we're dealing with something

00:07:11.067 --> 00:07:12.306
