00:08:00.807 --> 00:08:04.508
So this right over here is going
to be our general solution,

00:08:04.508 --> 00:08:09.508
in the case where we start
with something that is hotter

00:08:09.744 --> 00:08:11.450
than the ambient room temperature.

00:08:11.045 --> 00:08:13.259
And if we want to look at the
case where something is cooler

00:08:13.664 --> 00:08:15.122
than the ambient room temperature,

00:08:15.122 --> 00:08:17.399
so that's the situation,
let's say T is less than

00:08:17.399 --> 00:08:19.050
