00:08:19.005 --> 00:08:21.602
Then the absolute value of
T, then this thing over here

00:08:21.647 --> 00:08:24.221
is going to be negative, and
so the absolute value of it's

00:08:24.221 --> 00:08:25.843
going to be the negative of that.

00:08:25.843 --> 00:08:30.843
